Title: Aprilia 650 Pegaso 1999-2000 - Service Kit With NGK Plugs, Super 4
Description:
Oil, Oil Filter, Air Filter and Spark Plug/s Service Kit.

What you will receive:

Silkolene Oil (eg Super 4 / Comp 4 as stated in the title)
Hiflo Oil Filter
Hiflo Air Filter
NGK Spark Plug/s

Oil, Oil Filter, Air Filter and Spark Plug/s Service Kit.

What you will receive:

Silkolene Oil (eg Super 4 / Comp 4 as stated in the title)
Hiflo Oil Filter
Hiflo Air Filter
NGK Spark Plug/s

Here we have a service kit consisting of enough oil to complete a service, an oil filter, a Hiflo air filter and the relevant NGK spark plugs for the selected motorcycle.

The oil, filters and plugs are all that of a recognised premium brand and you will receive the oil type as stated in this listing title. 



*please note that you will only receive an oil filter if your motorcycle has one, as some models only have washable strainers and only the relevant amount of spark plugs and quantity of oil.

All other service items available separately, Please do not hesitate to ask for any further information.

All items sent are fully tracked and will require a signature
